                <span class="text">
               	<h1>Reliable Storage</h1>
                    Unlike other decentralized solutions, storage nodes are paid for their work in Bitcloud. This means data storage is reliable. Any node can sell their storage services at their preferred rate.
                </span>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
